Class EnvelopeEncoder

java.lang.Object
  cascom.fipa.envelope.EnvelopeEncoder
All Implemented Interfaces:
cascom.fipa.acl.ACLConstants, EnvelopeConstants
public class EnvelopeEncoder
extends java.lang.Object
implements EnvelopeConstants, cascom.fipa.acl.ACLConstants

Implements an encoder for bit-efficient envelopes as specificied in FIPA Specification number 88 (FIPA Agent Message Transport Envelope in Bit-Efficient Encoding Specification). The specification is available at URL:

Author:
Heikki Helin , Ahti Syreeni
